gical diagnostic results and post-operative complications are also often ignored. This book deals with complications and typical medical errors in surgery. It shows solutions and ways of dealing effectively with these errors and how to establish an efficient security management system.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 0aHealth facilitiesxRisk management. 0aMedical carexQuality control. 0aMedical errorsxPrevention. 4aBehandlungsfehler. 4aChirurgie. 4aOperative Fächer. 4aPatientensicherheit. 4aQualitätsmanagement. 7aMEDICAL / Diagnosis.2bisacsh  aMalpractice.  aMedical Quality Management.  aSurgery.1 aBlondel, Constantijn.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Medicine and Life Sciences 2000-2014 (EN)z978311023849508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Medicine and Life Sciences 2000 - 2014z9783110637915oZDB-23-GML08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2012z9783110288995oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PACKAGE  MEDICINE 2012z9783110293807oZDB-23-DME08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET MEDIZIN 2012z9783110293791oZDB-23-DMD0 cprintz978311027132440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311027160740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110271607423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110271607.jpg  a978-3-11-023849-5  DGBA Backlist Medicine and Life Sciences 2000-2014 (EN)c2000d2014  a978-3-11-023857-0  DGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1c2000d2014  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_MDPM  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_MDPM  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_STMALL  